{"tid":266629,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"鐵甲雄兵 (騎斬+控兵策略競技)","createTime":"2017-06-01T15:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T12:07:48.000Z","uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"07072f16e5d423dec2f6fd27bd26b0b1e6003bb7","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"依隻係一隻大陸遊戲<br />\n<a href=\"http://bos.ycgame.com/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbos.ycgame.com%2Findex.html&d=szf8fAl8O2y62Q6dS6kSoZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=d03811b3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bos.ycgame.com/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n係綜合 For Honor+騎斬+控兵策略咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但策略配合為主 技術其次 姐係唔太強調For honor/騎斬個種左右上下<br />\n<br />\n將能力有限反而兵力先重要 同埋佢操作好簡單 岩哂手殘但又想玩冷兵器game既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n兵種既配合先係致勝之道 隻game 分左步兵 弓兵 騎兵<br />\n步兵有分 盾兵/槍兵/雙手劍  盾兵負責開路cover弓兵 槍兵打騎兵下馬 雙手兵好抽得<br />\n弓兵 射程優勢 佔高位地利壓制 比近戰埋身就玩完<br />\n騎兵 搶點開路 遊走 屌打盾兵<br />\n<br />\n一場有5vs5 / 7vs7 每個玩家控一隻將同一隊兵咁玩 <br />\n一場大會戰就好天國驕雄/GOT 第9季 John Snow場雪地戰咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n勝利條件係地圖以佔點搶分/攻城/全滅對手咁<br />\n<img src=\"http://bos.ycgame.com/uploads/allimg/170421/1-1F421144A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbos.ycgame.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170421%2F1-1F421144A9.jpg&h=341ffbb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://bos.ycgame.com/uploads/allimg/170421/1-1F421144632.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbos.ycgame.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170421%2F1-1F421144632.jpg&h=27dc890b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://bos.ycgame.com/uploads/allimg/170421/1-1F421144410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbos.ycgame.com%2Fuploads%2Fallimg%2F170421%2F1-1F421144410.jpg&h=4ffa76cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然係大陸game 但唔會有課長出現 所有將都可以用game錢換到同冇得用點買<br />\n同埋新手送個d將都係有core作用 (盾兵/槍兵)<br />\n大家可以試下 好玩過虎x騎<br />\n多人玩可以開番個rc一齊玩"},{"pid":"e5094644111f96e71f291ae899199f3440f8246c","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"推下"},{"pid":"06931220ec3f90c8e26b44c66eab591367826bd4","tid":266629,"uid":32747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:48:02.000Z","msg":"Thx 想知隻game咩名好耐"},{"pid":"3095b1745afaff00a55dcc9e22110baf32f47e86","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Thx 想知隻game咩名好耐</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想玩可以一齊玩 唔駛聽班大陸仔講野"},{"pid":"4ad95ff020e14cfa0626418f08f2aec10046cce7","tid":266629,"uid":18416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:53:44.000Z","msg":"有冇單機？"},{"pid":"052ae1935f2db88c914f6b606369008b28ee57be","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇單機？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有pve mode不過唔係成日開<br />\n信我打人唔太駛考個人技術 控兵得f1 f2 3 4 幾隻制<br />\n同其他人兵種上配合同行動先重要"},{"pid":"c8c21a3127a3e01efcb8fc51f2edfb053012894a","tid":266629,"uid":51269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:29:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾 不如玩虎豹騎吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fcdae95003328fb6b209cba013be1209e3ea45","tid":266629,"uid":71433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:30:45.000Z","msg":"有沒挺遲問題？"},{"pid":"2153771a56c270380ca101f9087d005cc4e3e8e9","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾 不如玩虎豹騎吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n虎豹騎又要升兵 依家好難排到人 同埋對新手唔太friendly"},{"pid":"9e446a6f0cd4082eb1602e85bf814ba408e400a1","tid":266629,"uid":35866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T16:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockqu